{"type":"text","timestamp":1775850926458,"sessionID":"ses_28709eb33ffe4QxUWWcvbtz4rn","part":{"id":"prt_d78f693e3001NyR7c5u7EbF2SL","messageID":"msg_d78f689f7001gZHGprLflEkZMz","sessionID":"ses_28709eb33ffe4QxUWWcvbtz4rn","type":"text","text":"## AR-010 — Router 会话管理 Archive Summary\n\n### What was completed:\n\n**Core Session Package** (`pkg/router/session/`):\n- `types.go` - Session struct, SessionState, SessionConfig, RedisSessionConfig, GenerateSessionID()\n- `config.go` - Configuration with defaults and validation\n- `errors.go` - Error types (ErrSessionNotFound, ErrSessionExpired, etc.)\n- `metrics.go` - Prometheus metrics (active sessions, created, expired, duration, latency)\n- `manager.go` - SessionManager with Create/Get/Update/Delete/List/Cleanup operations\n- `memory_store.go` + test - In-memory SessionStore implementation\n- `redis_store.go` + test - Redis-backed SessionStore implementation\n- `session_test.go`, `manager_test.go`, `memory_store_test.go`, `redis_store_test.go` - Unit tests\n\n**Middleware** (`pkg/router/middleware/`):\n- `session_middleware.go` + test - Extract/attach session from cookie/header, WithSession wrapper\n\n**Router Integration**:\n- `session_handler.go` - HTTP handlers for session management endpoints\n- `session_resolver.go` - Session-aware route resolution with affinity\n- `resolver_session_test.go` - Session resolver tests\n\n**Documentation**:\n- `pkg/router/AR-010-session-management.md` - Complete design document (850 lines)\n- `pkg/router/session/doc.go` - Package documentation\n\n### What was deferred:\n\n**From proposal.md Out of Scope**:\n- WebSocket session management\n- Cross-region session replication\n- Session idle cleanup controller (agentd component)\n- Workload manager reconciler logic (separate controller)\n\n**From future considerations**:\n- Session affinity for multi-replica deployments (sticky sessions)\n- Per-session rate limiting\n- Session events (lifecycle hooks)\n- Cross-region session replication\n\n**Status**: Implementation complete for HTTP-based session management with Redis/memory persistence, session affinity routing, and full lifecycle management.","time":{"start":1775850926456,"end":1775850926456}}}
